\f3\i\fs66 \AppleTypeServices \cf6 \cb5 Trinity Nuclear Test\'92s Fallout Reached 46 States, Canada and Mexico, Study Finds\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa700\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0\b0\fs34\fsmilli17250 \cf6 \cb5 The research shows that the first atomic bomb explosion\'92s effects had been underestimated, and could help more \'93downwinders\'94 press for federal compensation.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qr\partightenfactor0

\fs19\fsmilli9750 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Credit...\cb1 \
